							<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-exclamation-sign" aria-hidden="true"></span>
							<span class="sr-only">Error:</span>
							<b>Delete account</b>
						</h3>
					</div>
					<div class="panel-body">
						<ul class="">
							<li class=""><p>Once you delete your account, there is no going back. Please be certain.</p></li>
							<li class="">
								<p>You will immediately lose access to your transaction history, account activity, and all other information associated with your account.</p>
							</li>
							<li class="">
								<p>Your payment information will be removed, and your username will be available to anyone signing up for a new account</p>
							</li>
							<li class="">
								<strong>This cannot be undone.</strong>
							</li>
						</ul>
						
						<div class="form-group col-md-9">
							<a href="#">
				  		    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default btn-delete">
								<strong>Delete my account</strong>
							</button>
							</a>
